{
  "version": "0.4",
  "title": "XCP Service: Brand Photography — Sub-page",
  "type": "page",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "brand_hero",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Brand Photography Hero",
        "layout": "full_width",
        "background_image": {
          "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/brand-photography-hero.jpg"
        },
        "content_position": "middle"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "brand_hero_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "brand_eyebrow",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Brand Photography Session</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_title",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Imagery That Tells Your Brand Story",
                "header_size": "h1",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_subtitle",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>A focused brand photography session designed to give you a complete library of professional images that reflect who you are, what you do, and the clients you want to attract. From £1,495.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_cta_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Enquire About Your Brand Session",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/contact",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "brand_overview",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Brand Photography Overview",
        "layout": "boxed",
        "structure": "20"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "brand_overview_text_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 60,
            "_column_size_tablet": 100,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "brand_overview_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "What a Brand Photography Session Includes",
                "header_size": "h2"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_overview_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>A brand photography session with XCP Photography is more than a shoot — it is a strategic visual content creation day built around your business goals.</p><p>We begin with a pre-shoot creative consultation to understand your brand, your audience, and your content needs. On the day, we work through a planned shot list covering portraits, lifestyle, product, workspace, and detail shots tailored to your brand identity.</p><ul><li>Pre-shoot creative brief and location scouting</li><li>Full day or half day shoot options</li><li>Multiple look and location changes</li><li>Up to 80 edited digital images (full day)</li><li>24–48 hour turnaround on your gallery</li><li>Commercial usage licence included</li><li>Optional: hair and makeup coordination</li></ul>"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "brand_overview_image_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 40,
            "_column_size_tablet": 100,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "brand_overview_image",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "image",
              "settings": {
                "image": {
                  "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/brand-photography-overview.jpg"
                },
                "image_size": "large"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "brand_investment",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Investment",
        "layout": "boxed"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "brand_investment_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "brand_investment_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Investment",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_investment_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Brand photography sessions start from <strong>£1,495</strong>. This is a qualifying investment — it reflects the level of creative and commercial commitment required to produce imagery that genuinely moves your business forward.</p><p>The average XCP brand photography project runs between £3,500 and £5,000, reflecting the full scope of a multi-location, multi-look session with pre-shoot consultation and post-shoot editing to publication standard. Hair, makeup, videography, and location hire are quoted separately based on your needs.</p><p>A detailed proposal with transparent pricing is provided after your discovery call — no surprise costs, no pressure.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_investment_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Start Your Enquiry",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/contact",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "brand_portfolio_samples",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Brand Photography Portfolio Samples",
        "layout": "boxed"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "brand_portfolio_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "brand_portfolio_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Recent Brand Photography Work",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_portfolio_note",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\">Add an Elementor Gallery widget here filtered to your 'Brand Photography' portfolio category. Go to Widget → Gallery, or use the Portfolio widget if you have Elementor Pro.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_portfolio_cta_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "View Full Portfolio",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/portfolio",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "brand_closing_cta",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Brand Photography Closing CTA",
        "layout": "boxed"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "brand_closing_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "brand_closing_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Ready to Tell Your Brand Story?",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_closing_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Enquire today. I respond personally within 24 hours and we will start with a no-pressure discovery call to see whether we are the right fit.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "brand_closing_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Enquire Now",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/contact",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
